race.comment: NEED YOU NOW (1) is boxed nicely on the inside. Latest effort finished 6th in a Grade 5 on October 17 over 300m at Healesville behind Fast Love beaten 5 lengths (17.12). Suited here and can find winning form. MIGHTY HERCULES (2) was below best at his last couple, the latest finishing eighth at Healesville, but was among the placings at this track three back. Can turn it around this time. PHANTOM DONALD (7) recorded his best time this course and distance last start, taking a Mix 6/7 in 26.47 by 0.6 lengths. Bold showing expected again. BLACK IN STYLE (6) should be thereabouts.
